":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:55:03.000Z","msg":"呢條友見袁國防潛晒法仲唔收聲"},{"pid":"cb71d02168ef0d55147741eb896a69912fae15f7","tid":1983924,"uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"幫手維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就黎6月 <br />\n<br />\n何栢良: 最好呢一年都戒嚴 商家你死你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da832448d3d3eef6c88ea52f0131cdc6d1d727f9","tid":1983924,"uid":196329,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32fa164a0cf42dbbfdae3aa54e4000502176d248","tid":1983924,"uid":39365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"28日係安全, 但好多行業未必頂到28日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"何栢良呢d只會從醫學角度出發<br />\n從醫學出發最穩陣唔好話28日<br />\n最好全部鋪唔準營業1年，所有人強制隔離屋企入面唔俾出街添<br />\n<br />\n但現實角度香港已經算控制得好好<br />\n而再拖落去到時經濟崩潰失業潮對社會帶黎既傷害<br />\n仲大過病毒傷害<br />\n所以點解美國爆到七彩<br />\n侵侵已經講緊要復工<br />\n你係醫生，大把錢，又冇失業危機<br />\n梗係下巴輕輕<br />\n同埋屌人行山撚啊去街撚啊<br />\n完全冇體諒過人既注意力同忍耐力係有個限度<br />\n由1月尾開始講關鍵14日，香港地方又細<br />\n佢地個個住大屋，又體唔體會到一般市民屈係咁細環境係咩感受？"},{"pid":"198dec84a88591909d43c39c926f52ff91237e60","tid":1983924,"uid":63838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"612 71 721前28日中共放返幾隻病毒人落香港幫手永續禁聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5c8aeb17bada619a136247f7180b1a3dc71e66","tid":1983924,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32fa164a0cf42dbbfdae3aa54e4000502176d248","tid":1983924,"uid":39365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"28日係安全, 但好多行業未必頂到28日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"唔係28日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係Day N+連續28日<br